name: cartaz/memória
description:
This is the poster I made using an all analog process for the debut show of my band FACAS. On this day, also played the bands Cäbränegrä, Böriz Kasööy and the noise artist Bukabog. A loud night for everyone.
This event took place at "Casinha", one of the main venues for underground artists in the city of Curitiba, Brazil. Unfortunately, the space had to shut down and be unoccupied due to imobiliary speculation in the region.
Besides a sentimental value for the day, this art piece is a way to remember that place where I already played a few times and where I watched so many other shows.
